<section>
  <h2>About the Camp</h2>
  <p>
    QC Elite STL Youth Basketball Camp is a three-week, high-intensity development program
    designed for young athletes in the St. Louis area who want to improve their game,
    confidence, and basketball IQ. This camp focuses on skill development, fundamentals,
    conditioning, and competitive play in a positive and disciplined environment.
  </p>

