<section class="leader">
  <h2>Camp Director: Quentin Coleman (QC)</h2>
  <p>
    The camp is led by Quentin “QC” Coleman, one of the best high school basketball players
    in America. A nationally ranked athlete from Principia High School, QC has competed
    at the highest levels of youth and high school basketball and brings elite-level
    experience directly to St. Louis youth.
  </p>
  <p>
    QC’s leadership, work ethic, and knowledge of the game set the standard for this camp.
    Campers will learn directly from someone who understands what it takes to compete
    nationally while staying grounded, disciplined, and focused.
  </p>
</section>

